<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_04_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema614_04_0004.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema614_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema614_04_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">직사각형 모양의 메모지가 3장 있습니다. 메모지의 가로에 대한 세로의 비율을 비교해 봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">가로에 대한 세로의 비를 쓰고, 비율을 분수와 소수로 각각 나타내어 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="flex align_start">
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="box box1">
                  <div class="img img1">
                    <span class="num">가</span>
                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content1.png" alt="" />
                    <span class="text_num num1">3 ㎝</span>
                    <span class="text_num num2">5 ㎝</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="img img2">
                    <span class="num">나</span>
                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content2.png" alt="" />
                    <span class="text_num num1">6 ㎝</span>
                    <span class="text_num num2">5 ㎝</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="img img3">
                    <span class="num">다</span>
                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content3.png" alt="" />
                    <span class="text_num num1">10 ㎝</span>
                    <span class="text_num num2">6 ㎝</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box box2">
                  <div class="table_box">
                    <table>
                      <colgroup>
                        <col style="width: 180px" />
                        <col style="width: 180px" />
                        <col style="width: 300px" />
                        <col style="width: 300px" />
                        <col style="width: 300px" />
                      </colgroup>
                      <thead>
                        <tr>
                          <th lang="y" scope="col" colspan="2">메모지</th>
                          <th lang="y" scope="col">가</th>
                          <th lang="y" scope="col">나</th>
                          <th lang="y" scope="col">다</th>
                        </tr>
                      </thead>
                      <tbody>
                        <tr>
                          <th lang="y" scope="row" colspan="2">가로에 대한 세로의 비</th>
                          <td>
                            <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="3 : 5"></math-field>
                            </div>
                          </td>
                          <td>
                            <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="6 : 5"></math-field>
                            </div>
                          </td>
                          <td>
                            <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="6 : 10"></math-field>
                            </div>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <th lang="y" scope="rowgroup" rowspan="2">비율</th>
                          <th lang="y" scope="row">분수</th>
                          <td>
                            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="(3)/(5)" text-align="center"></math-field>
                            </div>
                          </td>
                          <td>
                            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="(6)/(5)" text-align="center"></math-field>
                            </div>
                          </td>
                          <td class="multiple_answers">
                            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="(6)/(10)" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["(6)/(10)", "(3)/(5)"]}' data-multi-hint="y" text-align="center"></math-field>
                            </div>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <th lang="y" scope="row">소수</th>
                          <td>
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="0.6"></math-field>
                            </span>
                          </td>
                          <td>
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="1.2"></math-field>
                            </span>
                          </td>
                          <td>
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                              <math-field data-answer-single="0.6"></math-field>
                            </span>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y">비율이 같은 메모지를 찾아 기호를 고르세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="box box1 boolean_wrap">
                <div class="img img1">
                  <button data-answer-single="true" class="num">가</button>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content1.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">3 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">5 ㎝</span>
                </div>
                <div class="img img2">
                  <button data-answer-single="false" class="num">나</button>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content2.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">6 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">5 ㎝</span>
                </div>
                <div class="img img3">
                  <button data-answer-single="true" class="num">다</button>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content3.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">10 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">6 ㎝</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="page page_3">
            <h3 lang="y">비율이 1보다 작은 메모지와 1보다 큰 메모지를 찾아 각각 기호를 고르세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="box box1">
                <div class="img img1">
                  <span class="num">가</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content1.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">3 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">5 ㎝</span>
                </div>
                <div class="img img2">
                  <span class="num">나</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content2.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">6 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">5 ㎝</span>
                </div>
                <div class="img img3">
                  <span class="num">다</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content3.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">10 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">6 ㎝</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="box box2 boolean_wrap">
                <div class="box_row row1">
                  <div class="box_col col1">
                    <span class="f32b">비율이 1보다 작은 메모지</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="box_col col2">
                    <button data-answer-single="true" class="num">가</button>
                    <button data-answer-single="false" class="num">나</button>
                    <button data-answer-single="true" class="num">다</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box_row row2">
                  <div class="box_col col1">
                    <span class="f32b">비율이 1보다 큰 메모지</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="box_col col2">
                    <button data-answer-single="false" class="num">가</button>
                    <button data-answer-single="true" class="num">나</button>
                    <button data-answer-single="false" class="num">다</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_4">
            <h3 lang="y">앞에서 나타낸 비율을 비교하며 알게 된 점을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box">
              <div class="box box1">
                <div class="img img1">
                  <span class="num">가</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content1.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">3 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">5 ㎝</span>
                </div>
                <div class="img img2">
                  <span class="num">나</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content2.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">6 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">5 ㎝</span>
                </div>
                <div class="img img3">
                  <span class="num">다</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0004_content3.png" alt="" />
                  <span class="text_num num1">10 ㎝</span>
                  <span class="text_num num2">6 ㎝</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="speech_bubble">
                <div class="bubble_txt">
                  가로에 대한 세로의<br />
                  비율이 1이면 메모지는<br />
                  어떤 모양일까?
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <p lang="y">가로와 세로가 다르더라도 비율은 같을 수 있습니다.​</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
